descriptionHtml:
Kaede

[img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/78131-0-1471964607.jpg[/img]

Age: 22
Race: Breton

Kaede has a special talent with magic. She was taken away from
her family at the age of 15 by the  College of Winterhold. In the past
seven years, the college has conducted many experements on Kaede
to determine the source of her immense magic power. Kaede dreams
of the day she can break free from the college and return to
Dragon's Bridge to see her family again.

[u][b]Mods Used[/b][/u]
Hair: SG Hairs (required - not on the nexus)
Face & Body Texture:  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/76405]Girl of the Innocence[/url]
Eyes:  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13076]Cute Eyes[/url]
Eybrows:[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327] SG Female Eyebrows[/url]
Outfit: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/74702] VS Medieval Archeress Dress[/url]

This preset requires the [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624]Racemenu[/url] mod.

[u]How to Install:[/u]
Extract the contents of the zip file to the skyrim folder.
